<problem id="fs-id1766162"><para id="fs-id1540155">Which of the following is the most important buffer inside red blood cells?</para>
<list id="fs-id2071594" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>plasma proteins</item>
<item>hemoglobin</item>
<item>phosphate buffers</item>
<item>bicarbonate: carbonic acid buffer</item>
</list>
</problem>
